ActCanadian Wheat Board Act
SubjectDESIGNATED BARLEY - 2009-2010 UNSOLD STOCK ** Transfer to 2010-2011 Pool **
PrecisAuthority for THE CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD to transfer the DESIGNATED BARLEY unsold from the preceding pool that began on August 1, 2009, and ended on July 31, 2010, to the current pool period that began on August 1, 2010, and will end on July 31, 2011.
